INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('770', '12', '2016-06-03 10:34:25', '2016-06-03 02:34:25', '   <p><strong>1、Taylor Otwell</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-taylor-otwell.jpg\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>这个还需要介绍吗？好吧，<a href=\"http://laravelacademy.org/tags/laravel\" title=\"View all posts in Laravel\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel</a>框架是他写的。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/taylorotwell\" target=\"_blank\">@taylorotwell</a> 个人博客：<a href=\"http://taylorotwell.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://taylorotwell.com/</a> LinkedIn：<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/taylor-otwell-23794592\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/taylor-otwell-23794592</a></pre> <p><strong>2、Jeffrey Way</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-jeffrey-way.jpg\" width=\"256\" height=\"341\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>创建并维护<a href=\"http://laracasts.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Lastcasts</a>，这是一个教你学习Laravel和PHP的视频网站。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jeffrey_way\" target=\"_blank\">@jeffrey_way</a> GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/laracasts\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/laracasts</a> </pre> <p><strong>3、Matt Stauffer</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-matt-stauffer.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>活跃的Laravel博主，<a href=\"http://www.laravelpodcast.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel Podcast</a>创办者之一。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/stauffermatt\" target=\"_blank\">@stauffermatt</a> 个人网站&amp;博客：<a href=\"https://mattstauffer.co/\" target=\"_blank\">https://mattstauffer.co/</a> LinkedIn：<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/mattstauffer\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/mattstauffer</a> 即将推出的书： <a href=\"http://laravelupandrunning.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel: Up &amp; Running</a> </pre> <p><strong>4、Eric L. Barnes</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-eric-barnes.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>创办了<a href=\"https://laravel-news.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel News</a>博客，目前该博客已经升级为Laravel官方博客。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ericlbarnes\" target=\"_blank\">@ericlbarnes</a> 最新创建的博客：<a href=\"https://dotdev.co/\" target=\"_blank\">https://dotdev.co/</a> 个人博客：<a href=\"https://ericlbarnes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://ericlbarnes.com/</a> LinkedIn：<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/eric-barnes-19711167\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/eric-barnes-19711167</a> </pre> <p><strong>5、Dries Vints</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-dries-vints.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre><a href=\"http://laravel.io/forum\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel.io</a>社区的维护者，Lock作者，<a href=\"http://www.meetup.com/phpantwerp/\" target=\"_blank\">PHP Antwerp meetup</a>的组织者。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/driesvints\" target=\"_blank\">@driesvints</a> 个人网站&amp;博客：<a href=\"https://driesvints.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://driesvints.com/</a> LinkedIn：<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/driesvints\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/driesvints</a> </pre> <p><strong>6、Dayle Rees</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-dayle-rees.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>Laravel系列丛书作者：Code Happy、Code Bright、Code Smart。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/daylerees\" target=\"_blank\">@daylerees</a> 个人网站：<a href=\"http://daylerees.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://daylerees.com/</a> GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/daylerees\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/daylerees</a> 另一本很棒的书：<a href=\"http://daylerees.com/php-pandas/\" target=\"_blank\">PHP Pandas</a> </pre> <p>7、<strong>Adam Wathan</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-adam-wathan.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>开发者、作者、博主，<a href=\"http://www.fullstackradio.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Full Stack Radio</a>的创办者。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/adamwathan\" target=\"_blank\">@adamwathan</a> 个人博客：<a href=\"http://adamwathan.me/\" target=\"_blank\">http://adamwathan.me/</a> GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/adamwathan\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/adamwathan</a> 最近推出的书：<a href=\"http://adamwathan.me/refactoring-to-collections/\" target=\"_blank\">Refactoring to Collections</a> LinkedIn：<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/adam-wathan-9418984a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/adam-wathan-9418984a</a> </pre> <p><strong>8、Mahmoud Zalt</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-mahmoud-zalt.jpg\" width=\"362\" height=\"362\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>资深Web开发者、Laravel专家、Docker爱好者、开源倡导者，<a href=\"https://github.com/LaraDock/laradock\" target=\"_blank\">LaraDock</a>作者。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Mahmoud_Zalt\" target=\"_blank\">@Mahmoud_Zalt</a> 个人博客：<a href=\"http://www.zalt.me/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zalt.me/</a> </pre> <p><strong>9、Barry van den Heuvel</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-barry-van-den-heuvel.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>很多优秀Laravel扩展包的开发者，最著名的比如Laravel Debugbar和Laravel IDE Helper。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/barryvdh\" target=\"_blank\">@barryvdh</a> GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/barryvdh\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/barryvdh</a> LinkedIn：<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/barryvdheuvel\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/barryvdheuvel</a> </pre> <p><strong>10、Graham Campbell</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-graham-campbell.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>Laravel核心开发者，同样开发了很多Laravel扩展包，<a href=\"https://styleci.io/\" target=\"_blank\">StyleCI</a>的创建者。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GrahamJCampbell\" target=\"_blank\">@GrahamJCampbell</a> GitHub：<a href=\"https://github.com/GrahamCampbell\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/GrahamCampbell</a> 个人网站：<a href=\"https://gjcampbell.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">https://gjcampbell.co.uk/</a> </pre> <p><strong>11、Freek Van der Herten</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-freek-van-der-herten.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre><a href=\"https://murze.be/\" target=\"_blank\">Murze.be</a>博主。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/freekmurze\" target=\"_blank\">@freekmurze</a> 他公司的 Laravel&amp;PHP 开源项目：<a href=\"https://github.com/spatie\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/spatie</a> LinkedIn：<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/murze\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/murze</a> </pre> <p><strong>12、Marcel Pociot</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-marcel-pociot.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>Laravel传播者，开发了著名的Chrome扩展<a href=\"http://marcelpociot.com/blog/2016-03-21-laravel-testtools\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel Testtools</a>。  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcelpociot\" target=\"_blank\">@marcelpociot</a> 个人博客：<a href=\"http://marcelpociot.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://marcelpociot.com/</a> </pre> <p><strong>13、Shawn McCool</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-shawn-mccool.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre><a href=\"http://laracon.eu/2016\" target=\"_blank\">Laracon.EU</a>的组织者之一，创办了<a href=\"http://www.devdiscussions.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Dev Discussions podcast</a>  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ShawnMcCool\" target=\"_blank\">@ShawnMcCool</a> 个人博客：<a href=\"http://shawnmc.cool/\" target=\"_blank\">http://shawnmc.cool/</a> LinkedIn：<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/shawnmccool\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/shawnmccool</a> </pre> <p><strong>14、Chris Fidao</strong></p> <p><img src=\"http://www.ymroad.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/laravelpeople-chris-fidao.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\" alt=\"学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人\" /></p> <pre>创办了<a href=\"https://serversforhackers.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Servers for Hackers</a>，还写了本书<a href=\"https://leanpub.com/implementinglaravel\" target=\"_blank\">Implementing Laravel</a>  Twitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fideloper\" target=\"_blank\">@fideloper</a> 个人博客：<a href=\"http://fideloper.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://fideloper.com/</a></pre> <p>PS：你也可以在下面的评论中说出你心目中的Laravel<a href=\"http://laravelacademy.org/tags/%e7%89%9b%e4%ba%ba\" title=\"View all posts in 牛人\" target=\"_blank\">牛人</a>。</p>    ', '学习Laravel，你应该关注的14个国外 Laravel 牛人', '1、Taylor Otwell2、Jeffrey Way3、Matt Stauffer4、Eric L. Barnes5、Dries Vints6、Dayle Rees7、Adam Wathan', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e5%ad%a6%e4%b9%a0laravel%ef%bc%8c%e4%bd%a0%e5%ba%94%e8%af%a5%e5%85%b3%e6%b3%a8%e7%9a%8414%e4%b8%aa%e5%9b%bd%e5%a4%96-laravel-%e7%89%9b%e4%ba%ba', '', '', '2016-06-03 10:34:25', '2016-06-03 02:34:25', '', '0', 'http://www.ymroad.com/php/770.html', '0', 'post', '', '0');
